{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"URLSearchParams.get()","mdn_url":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/get","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URL_API\">URL API <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams\"><code>URLSearchParams</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Construtor</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/URLSearchParams\"><code>URLSearchParams()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Métodos</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/append\"><code>append()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/delete\"><code>delete()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/entries\"><code>entries()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/forEach\"><code>forEach()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><em><code>get()</code></em></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/getAll\"><code>getAll()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/has\"><code>has()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/keys\"><code>keys()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/set\"><code>set()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/sort\"><code>sort()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/toString\"><code>toString()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/values\"><code>values()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Páginas relacionadas a URL API</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/URL\"><code>URL</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>Esta é uma <a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Guidelines/Conventions_definitions#experimental\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tecnologia experimental (en-US)</a></strong><br>Verifique a <a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">tabela de compatibilidade entre Navegadores</a> cuidadosamente antes de usar essa funcionalidade em produção.</p></div>&nbsp;<p></p>\n\n<p>O métod&nbsp;<strong>get() </strong>&nbsp;da interface <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams\"><code>URLSearchParams</code></a>,&nbsp; retorna&nbsp;o primeiro valor associado ao parametro de busca fornecido.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">URLSearchParams.get(name)</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parâmetros","title":"Parâmetros","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"name\">name</dt>\n <dd>O nome do parâmetro à ser retornado.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"retorno","title":"Retorno","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Um <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>USVString</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> se o parâmetro de pesquisa for encontrado; Caso contrário, <code><strong>null</strong></code>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exemplo","title":"Exemplo","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Se a URL da sua página é&nbsp;<code>https://example.com/?name=Jonathan&amp;age=18</code> você&nbsp;pode obter o parâmetro&nbsp;'name' e 'age'&nbsp; usando:</p>\n\n<pre class=\"default prettyprint prettyprinted notranslate\"><code>let params = new URLSearchParams(document.location.search.substring(1));\nlet name = params.get(\"name\")<span class=\"kwd\">; // retorna a string \"Jonathan\"\n</span>let age = parseInt(params.get(\"age\"), 10<span class=\"kwd\">); // retorna o número 18</span></code>\n</pre>\n\n<p>Buscar um&nbsp;&nbsp;parâmetro que não esteja presente na string de pesquisa, retornará&nbsp;&nbsp;<code><strong>null</strong></code>:</p>\n\n<pre class=\"notranslate\"><code>let address = params.get(\"address\"); // null</code></pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificações","title":"Especificações","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Especificação</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://url.spec.whatwg.org/#dom-urlsearchparams-get\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">URL<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'get()' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Padrão em tempo real</span></td>\n   <td>Definição inicial.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect2\"><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect3\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect4\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div></div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari (WebKit)</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td>49.0</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Android Webview</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n   <th>Chrome for Android</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td>49.0</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td>49.0</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Exemplo","id":"exemplo"},{"text":"Especificações","id":"especificações"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility"}],"summary":"O métod get()  da interface URLSearchParams,  retorna o primeiro valor associado ao parametro de busca fornecido.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"URLSearchParams.get()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"URLSearchParams.get()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"URLSearchParams.get()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"URLSearchParams.get()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/api/urlsearchparams/get","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/api/urlsearchparams/get/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API","title":"APIs da Web"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams","title":"URLSearchParams"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/get","title":"URLSearchParams.get()"}],"